Promissory note for dates: <strong>B</strong> owes <strong>A</strong> 60 kor (10800 l) of dates. He is to pay the entire amount in Arahsamna (VIII). The earlier promissory note for 53 kor (9540 l) of dates is paid. 2 witnesses and the scribe (= <strong>B</strong>).<br />
