Receipt for silver, barley and dates: <strong>A</strong>&nbsp;receives from <strong>B</strong> 3 minas of cut silver of 1/8 alloy and 35 kor (6300 l) of dates from earlier promissory notes for silver, barley and dates. He gives back to <strong>B </strong>the promissory note related to this debt. It is recorded that <strong>A</strong> did not receive the barley. Each party has taken a copy of the document. 4 witnesses and the scribe: L&acirc;b&acirc;&scaron;i/Nab&ucirc;-nāṣir//Nann&ucirc;tu.<br />
